Class Bigram

  • java.lang.Object
    • smile.nlp.Bigram

  • public class Bigram
extends java.lang.Object
    Bigrams or digrams are groups of two words, and are very commonly used as the basis for simple statistical analysis of text. They are a special case of N-gram.
